Stable

- Dividend distribution (including to minorities) of about €4.2 billion in fiscal 2024 (increase of 45 cent per share to €4.70 from €4.25). For fiscal 2025, we estimate dividend distributions including minorities will increase further, to about €4.6 billion.

- Acquisition budget of about €2.5 billion per year.

- Cash outflow of up to €3.0 billion per year toward share repurchases under the new share buyback program, which has a volume of €6 billion, to be executed over the next five years.